(87, 1, '2020-08-30 21:14:44', '2020-08-30 21:14:44', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Memberships for the 2020/2021 season will open on 1 August 2020 and runs until 31 July 2020. Fees will be finalised in late July. Please wait until august to apply. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Step 1  Apply</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Apply or transfer you membership from another Club at Lifesaving Online.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If youre signing up as a family, remember to add all family members to the application.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The system will prompt you to set up an SLSA Member Area account. This is essential for club payments, renewals and change of details.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>if you are having trouble creating your accounts or would like more information, please open SLS- How to Join or Rejoin a club.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If youre applying for a transfer and you cant remember the last year you were a member at your previous club, call the SLSA Helpline at 1300 724 006.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Step 2- Pay</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At the end of this process you will be asked for payment. Click on the make Payment button that appears after you have submitted your application.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>OGSLSC fees are listed for you, and you must manually enter the amount. Please list the family surname in details.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please note that your membership application will not be progressed UNTIL payment is received. Do not wait for communication from OGSLSC before paying.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If youve missed the opportunity to pay on the SLSA joining page, you can do so via Members/Member Payments tabs on this website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Unpaid Application will be rejected after a few months</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Step 3- WWCC</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All members over 18 years of age must have a valid WWCC. Teachers and police offers are not exempt from this requirement.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Only social members (including parent of Surd Ed Nippers) do not require a WWCC you cannot assist with programs or access the changerooms. If your child(ren) becomes involved in Surf Sport, WWCC will be required.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>An existing WWCC must be updated to include Life Saving Victoria and OGSLSC.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The OGSLSC admin office must receive a hard copy WWCC assessment notice or an emailed copy of your MyCheck home screen before an adult membership will be processed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We encourage you to refer to further detail in the Working with Children Check tab under Memberships or visit <a href=\"http://www.workingwithchildren.vic.gov.au\">http://www.workingwithchildren.vic.gov.au</a> for more information.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n[contact-form-7 id=\"135\" title=\"Contact form 1\"]\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'How to Join', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-to-join', '', '', '2020-09-01 03:24:17', '2020-09-01 03:24:17', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=87', 0, 'page', '', 0),
