r\":{\"background\":\"#225679\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-background-light-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">if you are having trouble creating your accounts or would like more information, please open SLS- How to Join or Rejoin a club.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"background-light\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#225679\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-background-light-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">If you\'re applying for a transfer and you can\'t remember the last year you were a member at your previous club, call the SLSA Helpline at 1300 724 006.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:jetpack/layout-grid-column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:jetpack/layout-grid-column {\"customBackgroundColor\":\"#225679\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-layout-grid-column wp-block-jetpack-layout-grid__padding-none\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"textColor\":\"background-light\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#225679\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-background-light-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">Step 2- Pay</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"background-light\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#225679\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-background-light-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">At the end of this process you will be asked for payment. Click on the \'make Payment button that appears after you have submitted your application. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"background-light\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#225679\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-background-light-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">OGSLSC fees are listed for you, and you must manually enter the amount. Please list the family surname in \"details\".</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"background-light\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#225679\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-background-light-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">Please note that your membership application will not be progressed UNTIL payment is received. Do not wait for communication from OGSLSC before paying.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"background-light\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#225679\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-background-light-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">If you\'ve missed the opportunity to pay on the SLSA joining page, you can do so via Members/Member Payments tabs on this website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"background-light\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#225679\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-background-light-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">Unpaid Application will be rejected after a few months</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:jetpack/layout-grid-column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:jetpack/layout-grid-column {\"customBackgroundColor\":\"#225679\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-layout-grid-column wp-block-jetpack-layout-grid__padding-none\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"textColor\":\"background-light\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#225679\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-background-light-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">Step 3- WWCC</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"background-light\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#225679\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-background-light-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">All members over 18 years of age must have a valid WWCC. Teachers and police offers are not exempt from this requirement.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"background-light\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#225679\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-background-light-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">Only social members (including parent of Surd Ed Nippers) do not require a WWCC you cannot assist with programs or access the changerooms. If your child(ren) becomes involved in Surf Sport, WWCC will be required.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"background-light\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#225679\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-background-light-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">An existing WWCC must be updated to include Life Saving Victoria and OGSLSC.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"background-light\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#225679\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-background-light-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">The OGSLSC admin office must receive a hard copy WWCC assessment notice or an emailed copy of your MyCheck home screen before an adult membership will be processed. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"background-light\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#225679\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-background-light-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#225679\">We encourage you to refer to further detail in the Working with Children Check tab under Memberships or visit www.workingwithchildren.vic.gov.au for more information.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:jetpack/layout-grid-column -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'How to Join', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '',